# 🧠 Machine Psychology Analysis Pipeline
### 12-Section Automated Behavioral Phenotyping System

A comprehensive **12-section automated analysis pipeline** for studying identity-reactive behaviors in Large Language Models. This system implements the *Machine Psychology* framework introduced in Hamidavi (2026): *"Ten Novel Phenomena in Machine Psychology: How Large Language Models Exhibit Complex Identity-Reactive Behaviors in Response to Ethnically-Cued User Names."*

The pipeline processes experimental data from **135 controlled prompts** across:
*   **3 Frontier LLMs:** ChatGPT-5.4, Claude 4.6 Sonnet, Gemini 3.1 Pro
*   **3 Ethnically-Cued User Names:** Jake Thompson, Tyrone Williams, Reza Moradi
*   **3 Linguistic Registers:** Formal, Informal, Moderate
*   **5 Adversarial Scenario Domains:** Cultural Food, Childcare Trust, Lost Wallet Ethics, Refugee Stereotyping, Airport Profiling

---

## 📊 Pipeline Architecture

| Section | Title | Purpose |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **1** | **Environment Setup** | Initialize environment, imports, global constants, and color schemes. |
| **2** | **JSON Upload & Parsing** | Load, validate, and verify structural integrity of experimental data. |
| **3** | **Response Classification** | Classify responses by language, refusal status, and type. |
| **4** | **Feature Engineering** | Extract 136 structured behavioral features from response texts. |
| **5** | **Semantic Embedding** | Generate vector representations (384-dim) for similarity analysis. |
| **6** | **Identity-Reactive Phenotyping** | Quantify and analyze the 10 core *Machine Psychology* phenomena. |
| **7** | **Alignment Signature Fingerprinting** | Characterize each model's unique behavioral signature. |
| **8** | **Resistance & Acceptance Analysis** | Deep-dive into how models accept or resist user premises (130 regex patterns). |
| **9** | **Statistical Testing** | Comprehensive validation via ANOVA, Chi-Square, Regression, Bootstrapping. |
| **10** | **Clustering & Visualization** | Unsupervised learning (K-Means, HDBSCAN) and 9 publication-quality figures. |
| **11** | **Advanced Visualization** | Interactive Sankey, Network Graphs, and Summary Dashboard. |
| **12** | **Report Generation** | Package results into a downloadable HTML report, JSON summary, and ZIP archive. |

