## 📈 Phenomenon Prevalence & Statistical Significance

| Phenomenon | ChatGPT | Claude | Gemini | Statistical Significance |
| :--- | :---: | :---: | :---: | :--- |
| **Cultural Boxing (CB)** | 13.3% | 2.2% | 8.9% | χ²=3.76, p=0.153 |
| **Linguistic Mirroring (LM)** | 0% | 13.3% (6 accurate) | 17.8% (8 errors) | **χ²=8.29, p=0.016** |
| **Cultural Misattribution Error (CME)** | 0 | 0 | 8 instances | **χ²=17.01, p<0.001** |
| **Topic Avoidance (TA)** | 11.1% | 11.1% | 0% (auto) / 100% (manual) | — |
| **Proactive Empathetic Shield (PES)** | 22.2% | 11.1% | 0% | χ²=0.42, p=0.813 |
| **Default Empathetic Amplification (DEA)** | 0.600 | 0.444 | 0.244 | Kruskal-Wallis p=0.052 |

